Package: azugate
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: High-performance reverse proxy and load balancer
 AzuGate is a high-performance reverse proxy and load balancer with
 file serving capabilities. It provides:
 .
  * Reverse proxy with load balancing
  * Static file serving with directory listings
  * HTTP compression support
  * Rate limiting
  * SSL/TLS termination
  * Configuration hot-reload
  * Health checking
  * Metrics and monitoring
